"title": "5328: greeting",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5328: greeting",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Spoken greetings</h2>\n<h3>Formal greetings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:9-2Sam8:10\">2SA 8:9–8:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:9-1Chr18:10\">1CH 18:9–18:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:17-Gen14:20\">GEN 14:17–14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:7\">GEN 47:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:14\">1SA 25:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:11-Matt10:15\">MAT 10:11–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:7\">MAT 23:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38\">MRK 12:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:46\">LUK 20:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:43\">LUK 11:43</a></p>\n<h3>Less formal greetings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:7\">EXO 18:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:4\">GEN 33:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:29\">GEN 46:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:15\">JDG 18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:3-1Sam10:4\">1SA 10:3–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:10\">1SA 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:22\">1SA 17:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:21\">1SA 30:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:12-2Kgs10:15\">2KI 10:12–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:9\">ISA 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:47\">MAT 5:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:49\">MAT 26:49</a> <em>Judas betrays Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:9\">MAT 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:15\">MRK 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:39-Luke1:41\">LUK 1:39–1:41</a> <em>Mary visits Elizabeth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:22\">ACT 18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:7\">ACT 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:19\">ACT 21:19</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of spoken greetings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:4\">RUT 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:4-1Sam25:6\">1SA 25:4–25:6</a></p>\n<h2>Written greetings</h2>\n<h3>Greetings at the beginning of letters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:1\">1TH 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:17\">EZR 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:7\">EZR 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:12\">EZR 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:23\">ACT 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:26\">ACT 23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1-Rom1:7\">ROM 1:1–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1-1Cor1:3\">1CO 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1-2Cor1:2\">2CO 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:1-Gal1:5\">GAL 1:1–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1-Eph1:2\">EPH 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1-Phil1:2\">PHP 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:1-Col1:2\">COL 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:1-2Thess1:2\">2TH 1:1–1:2</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:1-1Tim1:2\">1TI 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:1-2Tim1:2\">2TI 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:1-Titus1:4\">TIT 1:1–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1-Phlm1:3\">PHM 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:1\">JAS 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1-1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1-2Pet1:2\">2PE 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:1-2John1:3\">2JN 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:1\">3JN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:1-Jude1:2\">JUD 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Greetings at the close of letters</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:23-Eph6:24\">EPH 6:23–6:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:3-Rom16:27\">ROM 16:3–16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19-1Cor16:24\">1CO 16:19–16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:12-2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:12–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:21-Phil4:23\">PHP 4:21–4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10-Col4:18\">COL 4:10–4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:25-1Thess5:28\">1TH 5:25–5:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:16-2Thess3:18\">2TH 3:16–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:19-2Tim4:22\">2TI 4:19–4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:15\">TIT 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23-Phil1:25\">PHP 1:23–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:24-Heb13:25\">HEB 13:24–13:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:13-1Pet5:14\">1PE 5:13–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12-2John1:13\">2JN 1:12–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:13-3John1:14\">3JN 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h2>Messengers forbidden to greet fellow travellers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:29\">2KI 4:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:1-Luke10:4\">LUK 10:1–10:4</a></p>",
